item.title: CVE-2017-17139|2024-08-05T20:43:59.752Z -- huawei%20technologies%20co.%2C%20ltd. -- mate%209%3B%20mate%209%20pro
item.description: Huawei Mate 9 and Mate 9 pro smart phones with software the versions before MHA-AL00B 8.0.0.334(C00); the versions before LON-AL00B 8.0.0.334(C00) have a information leak vulnerability in the date service proxy implementation. An attacker may trick a user into installing a malicious application and application can exploit the vulnerability to get kernel date which may cause sensitive information leak.
